---
title: Caprese-Inspired Chicken Flatbreads with Fresh Salad
description: We've taken the classic Capri combo and given it a new twist! With a mix of juicy chicken, marinated tomatoes, bocconcini and a hint of lemon, this dish is truly freshness in flatbread form!
